The villagers say Dr. Fah and Khru Prince are dating.

541
00:43:01,445 --> 00:43:03,428
The villagers are saying you're dating Khru Prince, is that true?

542
00:43:03,428 --> 00:43:04,798
What?

543
00:43:04,798 --> 00:43:06,939
If I really like Khru,

544
00:43:06,939 --> 00:43:09,039
will you be mad at me?

545
00:43:09,039 --> 00:43:11,904
I wish the pain…

546
00:43:11,904 --> 00:43:16,415
Turns into butterflies and flies away.

547
00:43:17,730 --> 00:43:22,610
♫ Do you believe that there is still hope for your love? ♫

548
00:43:22,610 --> 00:43:25,580
♫ Even in your dreams every night ♫

549
00:43:25,580 --> 00:43:30,790
♫ Love is still waiting for you to come and change your dreams ♫

550
00:43:30,790 --> 00:43:34,510
♫ So they can turn into reality ♫

551
00:43:34,510 --> 00:43:38,720
♫ If you're the sea, I'll be like the sand ♫

552
00:43:38,720 --> 00:43:44,870
♫ If you're the sky, please let me be the North star ♫

553
00:43:44,870 --> 00:43:49,190
♫ To guide your heart ♫

554
00:43:49,190 --> 00:43:55,270
♫ To be next to mine, like the sky and starlight ♫
